search_term: Find the official pricing page URL for OneNote (onenote.com). Only provide the exact URL to the pricing page, not a summary of pricing information.
response_text: OneNote does not have a standalone pricing page since it is free to use. You can explore additional details on its official website at [https://www.onenote.com](https://www.onenote.com).

extracted_content.content:
Microsoft OneNote

Your digital notebook

One cross-functional notebook for all your note taking needs.

![Image 1: Microsoft OneNote](https://site-cdn.onenote.net/161880740451_Images/home/new/top_v3.png)

![Image 2: Copilot in OneNote, supercharge your productivity](https://site-cdn.onenote.net/161880740451_Images/home/new/Copilot_v3.png)

Copilot in OneNote, supercharge your productivity

As your notetaking partner, Copilot in OneNote uses your prompts to draft plans, generate ideas, create lists, organize information, and more.

Sketch, annotate, and highlight freely

OneNote lets you combine the power of digital ink with the natural feel of a pen to help you sketch out your inspirations.

![Image 3: Sketch, annotate, and highlight freely](https://site-cdn.onenote.net/161880740451_Images/home/new/Inking_v3.png)

![Image 4: Share and Collaborate](https://site-cdn.onenote.net/161880740451_Images/home/new/Share_v3.png)

Share and Collaborate

Great minds don't always think alike, but they can share ideas and create together in OneNote.

Never miss a detail with voice transcription

Voice transcription makes it easier than ever to efficiently capture your notes, focus on what's important, and review your content later.

![Image 5: Never miss a detail with voice transcription](https://site-cdn.onenote.net/161880740451_Images/home/new/Transcription_v3.png)

![Image 6: OneNote in Education](https://site-cdn.onenote.net/161880740451_Images/home/new/Edu_v3.png)

OneNote in Education

Teachers can use OneNote to organize lesson plans in searchable digital notebooks, and staff can create a sharable content library. Encourage students to handwrite notes and sketch diagrams.
